Package: RLumCarlo
Type: Package
Title: Monte-Carlo Methods for Simulating Luminescence Phenomena
Version: 0.0.1
Date: 2017-01-27
Author: Johannes Friedrich [aut, trl, cre]
Authors@R: c(
